                            <comment id="74353" author="yujian" created="Sun, 5 Jan 2014 11:59:40 +0000"  >&lt;p&gt;Lustre client build: &lt;a href=&quot;http://build.whamcloud.com/job/lustre-b2_5/5/&quot; class=&quot;external-link&quot; target=&quot;_blank&quot; rel=&quot;nofollow noopener&quot;&gt;http://build.whamcloud.com/job/lustre-b2_5/5/&lt;/a&gt;&lt;br/&gt;
Lustre server build: &lt;a href=&quot;http://build.whamcloud.com/job/lustre-b2_4/70/&quot; class=&quot;external-link&quot; target=&quot;_blank&quot; rel=&quot;nofollow noopener&quot;&gt;http://build.whamcloud.com/job/lustre-b2_4/70/&lt;/a&gt; (2.4.2)&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;The same failure occurred:&lt;br/&gt;
&lt;a href=&quot;https://maloo.whamcloud.com/test_sets/a8e2dbf8-74f5-11e3-95ae-52540035b04c&quot; class=&quot;external-link&quot; target=&quot;_blank&quot; rel=&quot;nofollow noopener&quot;&gt;https://maloo.whamcloud.com/test_sets/a8e2dbf8-74f5-11e3-95ae-52540035b04c&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;Hi Oleg,&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;Could you please cherry-pick patch &lt;a href=&quot;http://review.whamcloud.com/8326&quot; class=&quot;external-link&quot; target=&quot;_blank&quot; rel=&quot;nofollow noopener&quot;&gt;http://review.whamcloud.com/8326&lt;/a&gt; to Lustre b2_5 branch? Thanks.&lt;/p&gt;</comment>
                            <comment id="72499" author="adilger" created="Thu, 28 Nov 2013 22:47:15 +0000"  >&lt;p&gt;Patch landed to master.&lt;/p&gt;</comment>
                            <comment id="71853" author="niu" created="Tue, 19 Nov 2013 06:58:40 +0000"  >&lt;p&gt;&lt;a href=&quot;http://review.whamcloud.com/8326&quot; class=&quot;external-link&quot; target=&quot;_blank&quot; rel=&quot;nofollow noopener&quot;&gt;http://review.whamcloud.com/8326&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/p&gt;</comment>
                            <comment id="71852" author="niu" created="Tue, 19 Nov 2013 06:46:25 +0000"  >&lt;p&gt;The connect_flags checking is wrong in test_209&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;div class=&quot;code panel&quot; style=&quot;border-width: 1px;&quot;&gt;&lt;div class=&quot;codeContent panelContent&quot;&gt;
&lt;pre class=&quot;code-java&quot;&gt;[[ $($LCTL get_param -n mdc.*.connect_flags) == ~disp_stripe ]] &amp;amp;&amp;amp; skip_env
&lt;/pre&gt;
&lt;/div&gt;&lt;/div&gt;

&lt;p&gt;will cooke a patch to fix it soon.&lt;/p&gt;</comment>
